WEBVTT

00:14:29.456 --> 00:14:32.176
Dopustite si agnosticizam

00:14:32.176 --> 00:14:34.871
i pritom mislim na stvari 
u kojima uživate.

00:14:34.871 --> 00:14:37.644
Lako je biti agnostik
u nekim područjima

00:14:37.644 --> 00:14:38.567
i biti zadovoljan,

00:14:38.567 --> 00:14:42.828
kao: "Agnostik sam
u pitanjima religije ili politike."

00:14:42.828 --> 00:14:47.040
Tako si možete dopustiti
dogmatizam u drugim područjima, zar ne?

00:14:47.040 --> 00:14:49.220
(Smijeh)

00:14:49.220 --> 00:14:50.290
Katkad,

00:14:50.290 --> 00:14:53.836
najveći intelektualci
izaberu jedno područje

00:14:53.836 --> 00:14:57.028
u kojem su potpuni dogmatici,
tako tvrdoglavo nerazumni,

00:14:57.028 --> 00:14:59.678
da pomislite: "Kako to mogu vjerovati?"

00:14:59.678 --> 00:15:04.170
No, to upija njihovu tvrdoglavost,